                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7794" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0304</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1718 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">梦想训练营：华远公司赋能员工释放价值活力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Training Camp of Dreams: Huayuan Company Empowers Employees to Release Value and Vitality</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒋宁，张薇薇，王艳波，苏家平，王晶晶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华远工程机械有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">梦想训练营；赋能；自我决定；内部动机；外部动机</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Training Camp of Dreams; Empowerment; Self determination; Internal motivation; External motivation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了华远公司通过价值观大讨论、结构整合、公开竞聘和“梦想训练营”等赋能措施，以期激发员工的“梦想”，改变华远公司部门结构僵化，员工缺乏学习动力和成长平台的问题。公司总经理刘明亮通过倾听、分析员工的“梦想”，运用PDCA循环管理法，成功地将“梦想训练营”打造为公司的“人才发展平台、干部培训基地和员工沟通桥梁”，满足了员工自主、胜任、关系三种基本心理需要，激发了员工的内部动机，促进外部动机内化为员工的内部动机，帮助员工实现了梦想，释放出价值活力。通过讨论学习华远公司“梦想训练营”激发员工梦想并帮助员工实现梦想的过程，可以更好地理解员工的基本心理需要，设计有针对性的赋能措施帮助员工释放价值活力。帮助学生掌握自我决定理论等关键理论知识点，培养学生的综合概括能力、理论联系实践的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes how Huayuan Company aims to stimulate employees to pursue dreams, and change the inflexible structure of departments and address the issue of employees lacking learning motivation and growth platforms through such empowerment measures as organizing a discussion of values, integrating structure, Opening competition process, and setting up “Training Camp of Dreams”. The general manager of the company, Liu Mingliang, successfully built the “Training Camp of Dreams” into the company’s “talent development platform, cadre training base, and employee communication bridge” by listening to and analyzing employees’ “dreams” and using the PDCA circular management method. It meets the three basic psychological needs of employee autonomy, competence and relationship, stimulates the internal motivation of employees, promotes the internalization of external motivation into the internal motivation of employees, helps employees achieve their dreams, and releases value vitality. By discussing and learning the process of Huayuan&#39;s &quot;Dream Camp&quot; to stimulate employees&#39; dreams and help employees realize their dreams, we can better understand the basic psychological needs of employees and design targeted empowerment measures to help employees release value vitality. It helps students master key theoretical knowledge points such as work motivation and self-determination theory, and cultivates students&#39; ability to comprehensively summarize and integrate theory with practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自我决定理论；赋能的内涵和形式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
